==Useful Info==
A '''green death''' is a [[poison]]-themed [[tier-2 demon]]. It likes to pelt you with high-powered [[Poison Magic]], but is otherwise not too dangerous. They can be found in [[Pandemonium]], [[the Abyss]], and one [[Swamp]] end.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
Even characters with [[poison]] resistance will take damage and get poisoned by their Poison Arrow spells (unless you're undead), but it still cuts the damage you take from them tremendously.

[[Category:Demon]]
